$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask GRHPI1 [GPI1]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "GRHPI1" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [GPI1] As [SIM_]
Grizo [GPI1]5
Grizo [GPI1]10
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [GPI1]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

